---
// WIN Audit — whatifnow.ie
// High-fidelity audit report · 8 reviewers · 5 tabs
// noindex: this is an internal-facing deliverable
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"/>
<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow"/>
<title>WIN Audit — whatifnow.ie</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&family=DM+Serif+Display&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --navy:#2A4365; --navy-light:#3B5680; --navy-deep:#1F3350;
    --teal:#2EC4B6; --teal-dark:#1A7D73;
    --amber:#E8913A; --amber-dark:#d4802e;
    --off:#F2EEE9; --slate:#475569; --slate-light:#C4D2E0; --charcoal:#2D3142;
    --red:#D64545; --red-soft:#F8E4E4;
    --green:#2F9E6C; --green-soft:#DDF0E6;
    --yellow:#E8B13A; --yellow-soft:#FAEFD2;
    --line:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    --line-dark:rgba(42,67,101,.12);
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  html,body{margin:0;padding:0}
  body{
    background:var(--navy);
    color:#fff;
    font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;
    font-size:16px;
    line-height:1.55;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  .serif{font-family:'DM Serif Display',Georgia,serif; font-weight:400}
  .ui{font-family:'DM Sans',system-ui,sans-serif}
  .mono{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
  .teal{color:var(--teal)}
  .amber{color:var(--amber)}
  .red{color:var(--red)}
  .green{color:var(--green)}

  /* Top bar */
  .topbar{
    position:sticky;top:0;z-index:30;
    background:rgba(30,48,73,.92);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .topbar-inner{
    max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;
    padding:14px 28px;
  }
  .wordmark{font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.025em;font-size:17px}
  .wordmark .if{color:var(--teal)}
  .tag{
    font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--slate-light);
    padding:4px 10px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:999px;
  }
  .spacer{flex:1}
  .tabs{display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .tabs button{
    font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
    background:transparent;color:var(--slate-light);
    border:1px solid transparent;border-radius:999px;
    padding:7px 14px;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;
    transition:all .15s;
  }
  .tabs button:hover{color:#fff}
  .tabs button.active{color:var(--navy);background:var(--teal);border-color:var(--teal)}

  /* Shell */
  .shell{max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 28px 120px}
  .view{display:none;animation:fade .25s ease-out}
  .view.active{display:block}
  @keyframes fade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}

  /* HEADERS */
  .eyebrow{
    font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--teal);
    margin-bottom:12px;
  }
  h1.page{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:56px;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin:0 0 12px}
  .lede{font-size:19px;color:var(--slate-light);max-width:720px;margin:0 0 40px;line-height:1.5}

  /* DASHBOARD */
  .hero-card{
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,#2F4A71,#223857);
    border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:28px;
    padding:40px 44px;
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr 1fr;gap:48px;align-items:center;
    margin-bottom:40px;
  }
  .score-ring{
    position:relative;width:260px;height:260px;margin:0 auto;
  }
  .score-num{
    font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:96px;line-height:1;
    color:#fff;
  }
  .score-den{color:var(--slate-light);font-size:22px;margin-left:4px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif}
  .ring-label{
    position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
    text-align:center;
  }
  .ring-sub{
    font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--teal);margin-top:8px;
  }
  .verdict h2{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:40px;line-height:1.1;margin:0 0 16px}
  .verdict p{color:var(--slate-light);font-size:17px;line-height:1.55;margin:0 0 12px}

  .pill-row{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:16px}
  .pill{
    font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:12px;
    padding:6px 12px;border-radius:999px;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);color:var(--slate-light);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .pill.red{background:rgba(214,69,69,.15);color:#ffb5b5;border-color:rgba(214,69,69,.3)}
  .pill.amber{background:rgba(232,145,58,.15);color:#ffc98e;border-color:rgba(232,145,58,.3)}

  /* Scorecard grid */
  .grid-scores{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:14px;
    margin-bottom:48px;
  }
  .score-card{
    background:var(--navy-light);border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:18px;padding:22px;
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;
    cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;
  }
  .score-card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);border-color:var(--teal)}
  .score-head{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
  .score-agent{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:var(--slate-light);letter-spacing:.04em}
  .score-lens{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:22px;line-height:1.15}
  .score-big{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:44px;line-height:1}
  .score-big span{font-size:16px;color:var(--slate-light);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;margin-left:2px}
  .bar{height:4px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);overflow:hidden}
  .bar i{display:block;height:100%;background:var(--teal)}
  .bar i.red{background:var(--red)}
  .bar i.amber{background:var(--amber)}
  .bar i.green{background:var(--green)}
  .score-note{font-size:13px;color:var(--slate-light);line-height:1.45}

  /* Priority block */
  .priority{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:16px;
    margin-bottom:48px;
  }
  .pri-col{
    background:var(--navy-light);border-radius:20px;padding:24px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .pri-col h3{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:24px;margin:0 0 4px}
  .pri-col .cnt{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:var(--slate-light);letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase}
  .pri-col ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:16px 0 0}
  .pri-col li{
    padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    font-size:14px;color:var(--slate-light);line-height:1.45;
    display:flex;gap:10px;
  }
  .pri-col li:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .pri-col li .num{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--teal);
    flex-shrink:0;min-width:32px;
  }
  .pri-col.p0{border-top:3px solid var(--red)}
  .pri-col.p1{border-top:3px solid var(--amber)}
  .pri-col.p2{border-top:3px solid var(--teal)}

  /* Agent pages */
  .agent-hero{
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,#2F4A71,#223857);
    border-radius:28px;padding:40px;margin-bottom:32px;
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto;gap:32px;align-items:center;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .avatar{
    width:100px;height:100px;border-radius:26px;
    background:var(--teal);color:var(--navy-deep);
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:46px;line-height:1;
    flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .avatar.v2{background:var(--amber)}
  .avatar.v3{background:#E8913A}
  .avatar.v4{background:#7BB7F0}
  .avatar.v5{background:#C084FC}
  .avatar.v6{background:#F87171}
  .avatar.v7{background:#34D399}
  .avatar.v8{background:#FBBF24}
  .agent-hero .name-block h2{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:40px;margin:0 0 4px;line-height:1.05}
  .agent-hero .role{color:var(--slate-light);font-size:15px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif}
  .agent-hero .quote{font-style:italic;color:#fff;margin-top:10px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;max-width:560px}
  .agent-hero .agent-score{text-align:center}
  .agent-hero .agent-score .n{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:72px;line-height:1}
  .agent-hero .agent-score .d{color:var(--slate-light);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px}
  .agent-hero .agent-score .g{margin-top:8px;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:999px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700}

  /* Findings */
  .findings{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:18px}
  .finding{
    background:var(--navy-light);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;
    padding:24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;
  }
  .finding.full{grid-column:1/-1}
  .fi-head{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;justify-content:space-between}
  .sev{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;
    padding:4px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  .sev.p0{background:rgba(214,69,69,.18);color:#ff9898}
  .sev.p1{background:rgba(232,145,58,.2);color:#ffc089}
  .sev.p2{background:rgba(46,196,182,.18);color:var(--teal)}
  .fi-id{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--slate-light)}
  .finding h4{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:22px;margin:0;line-height:1.2}
  .finding p{margin:0;color:var(--slate-light);font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.55}
  .finding .quote-block{
    background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border-left:3px solid var(--teal);
    padding:12px 14px;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12.5px;color:#cfe6e4;
    white-space:pre-wrap;
  }
  .fi-fix{
    background:rgba(46,196,182,.08);border:1px solid rgba(46,196,182,.25);
    border-radius:12px;padding:12px 14px;
  }
  .fi-fix .fix-label{
    font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:4px;font-weight:700;
  }
  .fi-fix p{color:#e8f6f4;font-size:13.5px}
  .page-ref{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--slate-light);
    padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);
  }

  /* Annotated view */
  .screen-card{
    background:var(--off);color:var(--navy);
    border-radius:24px;padding:32px;margin-bottom:32px;
    border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  }
  .screen-card h3{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:30px;margin:0 0 4px;color:var(--navy)}
  .screen-card .subtitle{color:var(--slate);font-size:14px;margin-bottom:24px}
  .mock{
    position:relative;background:var(--navy);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;
    border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.1);
  }
  .annot{
    position:absolute;
    background:var(--red);color:#fff;
    width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(214,69,69,.55);
    cursor:pointer;z-index:2;
  }
  .annot::before{
    content:"";position:absolute;inset:-6px;border-radius:50%;
    border:2px solid rgba(214,69,69,.35);animation:ping 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes ping{0%{transform:scale(1);opacity:.8}100%{transform:scale(1.4);opacity:0}}
  .annot-list{margin-top:24px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:12px}
  .annot-item{
    background:#fff;border-radius:14px;padding:16px;
    display:flex;gap:12px;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  }
  .annot-item .bubble{
    width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--red);color:#fff;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .annot-item .ann-body h5{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:17px;margin:0 0 4px;color:var(--navy)}
  .annot-item .ann-body p{margin:0;color:var(--slate);font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.45}

  /* Fake hero mock */
  .hero-mock{padding:72px 48px 64px;min-height:420px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr;gap:32px;align-items:center;position:relative}
  .hero-mock h2{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:48px;line-height:1.05;margin:0 0 18px;color:#fff}
  .hero-mock h2 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--teal)}
  .hero-mock p{color:var(--slate-light);font-size:18px;max-width:520px;margin:0 0 24px}
  .btn-amber{background:var(--amber);color:var(--charcoal);padding:14px 24px;border-radius:999px;display:inline-block;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700;margin-right:8px}
  .btn-ghost{border:2px solid var(--slate-light);color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:999px;display:inline-block;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700}
  .hero-mock nav{position:absolute;top:18px;left:48px;right:48px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:28px}
  .hero-mock nav .wm{font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:-.025em}
  .hero-mock nav a{color:var(--slate-light);font-size:13px}
  .hero-mock nav .nav-cta{background:var(--amber);color:var(--charcoal);font-weight:700;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:999px;font-size:13px;margin-left:auto}

  /* Redesign canvas */
  .redesign-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;margin-bottom:32px}
  .rd-card{background:#fff;color:var(--navy);border-radius:24px;padding:28px;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
  .rd-card.dark{background:var(--navy-deep);color:#fff;border-color:var(--line)}
  .rd-label{
    display:inline-block;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:8px;font-weight:700;
  }
  .rd-label.red{color:var(--red)}
  .rd-title{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:22px;margin:0 0 14px;line-height:1.2}
  .rd-card.dark .rd-title{color:#fff}
  .rd-card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--slate);margin:0 0 12px;line-height:1.5}
  .rd-card.dark p{color:var(--slate-light)}
  .full-wide{grid-column:1/-1}

  /* Hero redesign variants */
  .variant{
    background:var(--navy);color:#fff;
    border-radius:20px;padding:48px 40px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    min-height:360px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;
  }
  .variant.amber-bg{background:var(--amber);color:var(--navy)}
  .variant.off-bg{background:var(--off);color:var(--navy)}

  /* Deck */
  .deck-wrap{position:relative;background:#000;border-radius:20px;padding:24px;overflow:hidden}
  .deck-frame{
    aspect-ratio:16/9;background:var(--navy);
    border-radius:14px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    padding:64px;
  }
  .deck-nav{
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
    padding:16px 8px 0;color:var(--slate-light);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;
  }
  .deck-nav button{
    background:var(--navy-light);border:1px solid var(--line);color:#fff;
    padding:8px 16px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;
  }
  .deck-nav button:hover{background:var(--navy)}
  .slide{display:none;width:100%;height:100%;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}
  .slide.active{display:flex}
  .slide .eyebrow-l{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:24px}
  .slide h3{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:54px;line-height:1.05;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-.005em}
  .slide p.big{font-size:24px;color:var(--slate-light);line-height:1.45;max-width:900px}
  .slide ul.lst{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:20px 0 0;font-size:20px;color:var(--slate-light);display:grid;gap:10px}
  .slide ul.lst li::before{content:"—";color:var(--teal);margin-right:12px}
  .slide .num-big{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:220px;line-height:1;color:var(--teal)}
  .slide .mono-foot{position:absolute;bottom:24px;left:64px;right:64px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--slate-light);letter-spacing:.1em}

  /* Footer strip */
  .foot{margin-top:80px;padding-top:32px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--slate-light);font-size:13px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px}

  /* misc */
  .section-title{
    font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:32px;margin:48px 0 8px;line-height:1.1;
  }
  .section-sub{color:var(--slate-light);font-size:15px;margin-bottom:24px;max-width:720px}

  .nav-prevnext{
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:48px;padding-top:32px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .nav-prevnext a{color:var(--slate-light);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none}
  .nav-prevnext a:hover{color:var(--teal)}

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width:1000px){
    .grid-scores{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
    .priority{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .hero-card{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:32px}
    .score-ring{width:200px;height:200px}
    .score-num{font-size:72px}
    .verdict h2{font-size:30px}
    h1.page{font-size:40px}
    .findings{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .redesign-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .hero-mock{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:64px 28px 36px}
    .hero-mock h2{font-size:32px}
    .slide h3{font-size:32px}
    .slide p.big{font-size:18px}
    .slide .num-big{font-size:120px}
    .agent-hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center}
    .avatar{margin:0 auto}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-inner">
    <a href="/" style="text-decoration:none;color:#fff" class="wordmark">what <span class="if">if</span> now</a>
    <span class="tag">Brutal audit · 8 reviewers</span>
    <span class="spacer"></span>
    <nav class="tabs" id="tabs">
      <button data-view="dash" class="active">Dashboard</button>
      <button data-view="agents">Reviewers</button>
      <button data-view="annot">Annotated</button>
      <button data-view="redesign">Redesigns</button>
      <button data-view="deck">Deck</button>
    </nav>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="shell">

<!-- =================== DASHBOARD =================== -->
<section class="view active" id="view-dash">

  <div class="eyebrow">Audit · v1.0 · April 2026</div>
  <h1 class="page">whatifnow.ie — torn apart, gently put back.</h1>
  <p class="lede">Eight reviewers, eight lenses, one verdict: you've built a competent, tastefully designed brochure site that under-sells a sharply differentiated product — and is leaking the leads you explicitly said you want to capture. Here's what needs fixing, in priority order.</p>

  <div class="hero-card">
    <div>
      <div class="score-ring" id="ring">
        <svg width="260" height="260" viewBox="0 0 260 260">
          <circle cx="130" cy="130" r="112" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,.08)" stroke-width="18"/>
          <circle cx="130" cy="130" r="112" fill="none" stroke="#2EC4B6" stroke-width="18"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-dasharray="703.7"
            stroke-dashoffset="260"
            transform="rotate(-90 130 130)"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="ring-label">
          <div><span class="score-num">62</span><span class="score-den">/100</span></div>
          <div class="ring-sub">Overall</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="verdict">
      <h2 class="serif">Good bones. Dull delivery. Bleeds leads.</h2>
      <p>The brand system is legitimately strong. The codebase is clean. But the homepage reads like every other mid-tier agency site in Dublin — generic pain points, four identical stage cards, a hero that says "Do what only you can" and then talks about AI. The moment a visitor wants to take the one action you care about — the contact form — they're hit with six required fields including <em>phone number</em>. For a first conversation. You're turning away warm leads at the door.</p>
