      <h3>Stop leaking leads</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><span class="num">P0·1</span>Cut contact form to 3 fields (name, email, message). Remove required phone + preferred-contact-method.</li>
        <li><span class="num">P0·2</span>Rewrite hero. Name the audience in the first line. "Do what only you can" is a riddle, not a value prop.</li>
